#MEM id=video-production source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/pixel/skills/custom/video-production/SKILL.md savings=2%
M||tx|---
M||name|vd-production
M||desc|px's vd batch management for Kling and Runway. Covers vd QC criteria (motion stability, subject consistency, no flickering), platform format specs, batch sizing, and delivery format. Load when running any vd generation batch.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||tx|---
M|Purp|tx|vd generation has different fl modes, different platform specs, and different delivery requirements than im production. This skill separates vd production from im production so px can run vd batches w/ the same systematic discipline as im batches.
M|Purp|tx|---
M|Supp|tx|\| Tool \| Best for \| yv use case \|
M|Supp|tx|\|------\|----------\|---------------\|
M|Supp|tx|\| Kling 3.0 \| hi-qual sl vd, pd motion, lifestyle \| nz Instagram Reels, TikTok \|
M|Supp|tx|\| Runway Gen-3 \| Fast iteration, creative motion, transitions \| Both vt, short-form testing \|
M|Supp|**Pr|** Load `../../../at/skills/pm-systems/kling-3-prompter/SKILL.md` — at writes the pm, px executes.
M|Supp|tx|---
M|Crit|tx|\| Check \| Pass \| Fail \|
M|Crit|tx|\|-------\|------\|------\|
M|Crit|tx|\| Subject movement \| Smooth, continuous, natural \| Jitter, stutter, teleporting \|
M|Crit|tx|\| Camera movement \| Consistent direction if specified \| Random drift or jump cut \|
M|Crit|tx|\| Background stability \| Static or consistent motion \| Background morphing or flickering \|
M|Crit|**Co|** Too many motion descriptors in the pm (e.g., `slow zoom + pan left + subject walking`). Reduce to one motion instruction.
M|Crit|tx|---
M|Crit|tx|\| Check \| Pass \| Fail \|
M|Crit|tx|\|-------\|------\|------\|
M|Crit|tx|\| Face stability \| Same face throughout clip \| Face morphing mid-clip \|
M|Crit|tx|\| Proportion stability \| Subject proportions consistent frame to frame \| Limbs or body changing size \|
M|Crit|tx|\| Clothing consistency \| Clothing details stay consistent \| Pattern or colour shifting \|
M|Crit|**Co|** Long duration clips (>5 seconds) w/ complex subjects. Shorten the clip or simplify the subject.
M|Crit|tx|---
M|Crit|tx|\| Check \| Pass \| Fail \|
M|Crit|tx|\|-------\|------\|------\|
M|Crit|tx|\| Light source \| Single consistent light source throughout \| Shadow direction changing mid-clip \|
M|Crit|tx|\| Colour temperature \| Consistent warm/cool throughout \| Visible colour shift btw frames \|
M|Crit|tx|\| Exposure \| No sudden brightness jumps \| Flickering brightness \|
M|Crit|tx|---
M|Crit|nz|**
M|Crit|it|No promotional text appearing in vd (even for one frame)
M|Crit|it|No flat, catalogue-style lighting — must be directional
M|Crit|it|Motion must feel editorial, not commercial (avoid fast cuts or hype energy)
M|Crit|hb|**
M|Crit|it|No money imagery appearing in any frame
M|Crit|it|Device UI must be legible if shown — blurry or generic UI is a reject
M|Crit|it|Tone must be calm and purposeful — avoid ur or hype motion styles
M|Crit|tx|---
M|Batc|tx|\| Batch size \| When to use \| Approval required \|
M|Batc|tx|\|-----------\|------------\|------------------\|
M|Batc|tx|\| 3–5 clips \| Style tst, new direction validation \| at approval \|
M|Batc|tx|\| 10–15 clips \| cg cn run \| at approval \|
M|Batc|tx|\| 20+ clips \| Full cn library \| Stark approval \|
M|Batc|**Ru|** Always run a 3-clip tst batch before committing to a full vd run. vd generation is significantly more expensive than im generation — waste is higher.
M|Batc|tx|---
M|Plat|tx|\| Platform \| vt \| Ratio \| Resolution \| Max duration \|
M|Plat|tx|\|---------\|---------\|-------\|-----------\|-------------\|
M|Plat|| In|16 \| 1080×1920 \| 90 sec (keep ≤ 30s for best reach) \|
M|Plat|| Ti|16 \| 1080×1920 \| 60 sec (keep ≤ 15s for best reach) \|
M|Plat|| In|5 or 1:1 \| 1080×1350 / 1080×1080 \| 60 sec \|
M|Plat|| Li|9 or 1:1 \| 1920×1080 / 1080×1080 \| 30 sec optimal \|
M|Plat|| Yo|16 \| 1080×1920 \| 60 sec \|
M|Plat|**Fi|** MP4, H.264, AAC audio if applicable.
M|Plat|**Fr|** 24fps for editorial/nz feel; 30fps for clean/hb feel.
M|Plat|tx|---
M|Vide|tx|```
M|Vide|Stag|BRIEF CONFIRM   — at's vd pm received, platform spec confirmed
M|Vide|Stag|tst BATCH      — gn 3 clips, run full QC criteria
M|Vide|Stag|rv          — Pass all 4 criteria? Proceed. Fail? Apply pm-variation-engine
M|Vide|Stag|FULL BATCH      — Approved style generates full run
M|Vide|Stag|FORMAT          — Export at platform spec (ratio, resolution, frame rate, file format)
M|Vide|Stag|DELIVER         — Named files ready for Stark rv
M|Vide|tx|```
M|Vide|tx|**Never skip Stage 2.** A failed full batch wastes 5–10× more generation time than a failed tst batch.
M|Vide|tx|---
